ere av fritidsb\u00e5ter skal levere kasserte b\u00e5ter p\u00e5 godkjente mottak. \u00abEksempler p\u00e5 dette kan v\u00e6re innleveringspant, \u00e5rsavgift og lignende virkemidler\u00bb, skriver departementet.", "Det er uvisst hvor stort omfang en eventuell returordning vil f\u00e5. Dette skal ogs\u00e5 vurderes. If\u00f8lge opplysninger fra 2007 ble cirka 5.500 b\u00e5ter utrangert dette \u00e5ret."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|innenriks"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "10ab86c42cb3d09d73fc92840f576179155d1fde669ea1864019b4271a3f6d6b"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2014-09-22T06:53:13.838Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Vrakpant p\u00e5 kasserte fritidsb\u00e5ter skal f\u00f8rst utredes i mer enn ett \u00e5r."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article8811615.ece/ALTERNATES/w980-default/sy720b94.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/f80cb08f44ced48cfd83f26f09ed27ff457bd6f8.jpg?59771f37"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Vrakpant for fritidsb\u00e5ter tidligst i 2015 -adressa.no", "Milj\u00f8farlige stoffer", "Pant og \u00e5rsavgift"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "f80cb08f44ced48cfd83f26f09ed27ff457bd6f8"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "innenriks"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "hobbies-and-interests"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["b\u00e5ter", "fritidsb\u00e5ter", "kasserte fritidsb\u00e5ter", "kasserte"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["milj\u00f8direktoratet", "milj\u00f8verndepartementet"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "